  "Description": {
    "English": "Provides the Exosuit with <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced movement capabilities</span>, including temporary flight.<br><br>Control thrust with <span class=\"name name-img\">JUMP</span>. The flightpack uses energy from the <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Exosuit Life Support</span> system to pressurize and vent bursts of gas, propelling the user into the air.<br><br>Jetpack can be temporarily overloaded by gathering <span class=\"name name-technology\">Deuterium-rich plants</span>, causing a dramatic increase in available thrust.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "为套装提供<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级移动功能</span>，包括短暂飞行。<br><br>采用<span class=\"name name-img\">JUMP</span>来控制推进。飞行包使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">套装生命维持</span>系统的能量来增压和排出阵阵气体，从而将使用者推向空中。<br><br>可以通过收集<span class=\"name name-technology\">富氘植物</span>使喷气背包暂时获得过载能力，显著提升最大推力。",
    "TencentChinese": "为套装提供<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级移动功能</span>，包括短暂飞行。<br><br>采用<span class=\"name name-img\">JUMP</span>来控制推进。飞行包使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">套装生命维持</span>系统的能量来增压和排出阵阵气体，从而将使用者推向空中。<br><br>可以通过收集<span class=\"name name-technology\">富氘植物</span>使喷气背包暂时获得过载能力，显著提升最大推力。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使強化套裝獲得<span class=\"name name-technology\">進階移動能力</span>，包括短暫飛行。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">JUMP</span> 控制推進力道。飛行背包利用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">強化套裝維生</span>系統的能量，加壓並釋放氣體，將使用者推向空中。<br><br>收集<span class=\"name name-technology\">含氘量高植物</span>可以暫時使噴射背包超載，大幅提升可用的推進力量。"
  },
